{
  "chapter": "057",
  "title": "绛侯周勃世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "周勃出身",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周勃</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>人。其先人是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">卷</span>人，迁居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>以编织薄曲（蚕箔）为生，常替人吹箫给丧事用，又是一名能拉硬<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">材官</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "从征灭秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>作为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公初起兵时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中涓</span>身份跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>陵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方与</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方与</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛，与之交战，击退敌人。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span>邑。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>东。回军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">留</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">萧</span>。又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下邑</span>，率先登城。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span>五<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒙</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">虞</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车骑</span>，担任殿军。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">爰戚</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东缗</span>，一直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栗</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">齧桑</span>，率先登城。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军于阿下，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">濮阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甄城</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">都关</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛朐</span>，俘获<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">单父</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span>。夜<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">张</span>，继续向前到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">卷</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李由</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍丘</span>下。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">开封</span>，最先到城下战功最多。后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打败</span>并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>领兵东到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>。自初起<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>到回至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>，共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二月（时长）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚怀王\">怀王（楚怀王）</span>封<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">安武侯</span>，任<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>郡长。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">虎贲令</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">虎贲令</span>身份随<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公平〖◈定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东郡尉</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城武</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王离</span>军，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长社</span>，率先登城。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">缑氏</span>，截断<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河津</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵贲</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">尸北</span>。南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南阳守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕齮\">齮（吕齮）</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">峣关</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓝田</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "定三秦击楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>至，任命<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>爵为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">威武侯</span>。跟随进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>中，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。又回师平〖◈定三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>地，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐食邑</span>怀德。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">槐里</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">好畤</span>，战功居首。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵贲</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：内史保\">保（内史保）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，战功居首。北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漆</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章平</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">姚卬</span>军。西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汧</span>。回师<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郿</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">频阳</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">包围</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">废丘</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西丞</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>盗贼<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴</span>军，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上邽</span>。东守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">峣关</span>。转<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲逆</span>，战功居首。还守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追</span>击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项籍\">籍（项籍）</span>死后，因而东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>郡，共得二十二县。回师守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栎阳</span>，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">颍侯</span>共<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">锺离</span>。以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>身份跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>击<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>者<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">易下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>他。所率士卒挡住<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">驰道</span>战功最多。〖^赐爵</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，剖<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>世代相传不绝。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">绛</span>县八千一百八十户，号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "击韩王信",
      "text": "以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>身份跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>叛的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>地，招<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span>并<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霍人</span>。向前到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武泉</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>骑兵，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武泉</span>北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。转<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铜鞮</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。回师，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span>服<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>的胡骑兵于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">晋阳</span>下，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">晋阳</span>。后又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">硰石</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之，向北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追</span>击八十里。回师<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼烦</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三城</span>，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>骑兵于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>下，所率士卒挡住<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">驰道</span>战功最多。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>升任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "击陈豨卢绾",
      "text": "<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">屠</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>。所率士卒<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>乘<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>絺。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵利</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">楼烦</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之。俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>手下将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋最</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span>守。又转而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，俘获<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云中</span>守遫、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕肆</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将勋</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span>郡十七县，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云中</span>郡十二县。又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灵丘</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>，俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程纵</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈武</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高肆</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>郡九县。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>身份取代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>为将，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>并<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓟</span>，俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾将抵\">抵（卢绾将抵）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾相偃\">偃（卢绾相偃）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾守陉\">陉（卢绾守陉）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾尉弱\">弱（卢绾尉弱）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾御史施\">施（卢绾御史施）</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">屠</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浑都</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上兰</span>，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沮阳</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追</span>至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长城</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上谷</span>十二县，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">右北平</span>十六县，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽西</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>二十九县，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渔阳</span>二十二县。最终随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>共俘获<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>；另外<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>敌军二支，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span>城三座，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>郡五个，县七十九个，俘获<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将</span>各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "勃木强敦厚",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>为人质朴刚强敦厚，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>认为可以托付大事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>不好<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>，每次召见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸生</span>和游说之士，就面朝东坐而斥责说：\"赶快对我说事。\"他就是这样粗鲁少文。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "诛吕立文帝",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国归来时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>已驾崩，以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>身份事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>，设置<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>官，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十岁（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>驾崩。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕禄</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王身份为汉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕产</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吕王</span>身份为汉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，把持<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝大权，欲危及<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>身为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>，进不了军营大门。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>身为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，也不能理事。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>合谋，终于<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>灭<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>并<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>。其事详见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span>本纪。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "辞相就国",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>即位后，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>为右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，赐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千斤</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>。过了一个多月，有人劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>说：\"您既已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>，拥立<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>王，威震<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，而您又受厚赏，居尊位，被宠爱，久了必祸及自身。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>害怕，也自觉危险，就向皇上请辞交还相<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>。皇上答应。一年多后，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>去世，皇上又任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。十几个月后，皇上说：\"前些日子我下诏让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>回到封国去，有些人还未能执行，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>是我所倚重的，请他率先做个榜样。\"于是免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，就国。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "被诬下狱",
      "text": "过了一年多，每当<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>郡守尉巡行各县到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">绛</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>自己担心被诛，常穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>胄，命家人持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>器以待。后来有人上书告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>欲谋反，交给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>办理。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>把案子交到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，逮捕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>审理。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>害怕，不知如何答辩。狱吏渐渐侵辱他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>拿了千<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>送给狱吏，狱吏就在简牍背面写字给他看，说：\"以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>为证。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>的女儿，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>的太子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胜之</span>娶她为妻，所以狱吏教他找公主作证。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>受增封得到的赏赐，都送给了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄昭</span>。到被囚禁危急时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄昭</span>为他向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>求情，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>也认为他没有谋反事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>朝见，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>拿起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冒絮</span>（头巾）掷向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>，说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>身佩<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玺</span>、统领<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北军</span>时不谋反，现居一小县，反而要谋反吗！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>已看到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>的狱辞，就道歉说：\"官吏刚刚查验，马上就放出他。\"于是派使者持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span>免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>，恢复爵位食邑。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>出狱后说：\"我曾率百万大军，怎知狱吏如此尊贵！\""
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "绛侯传位",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>又回到封国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">武侯（周勃）</span>。子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胜之</span>继<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>侯。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六岁（时长）</span>后，娶了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>，关系不和，又犯了<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。断绝了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一岁（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>于是选择<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>诸子中贤能的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>，封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>，续<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>后嗣。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "许负相亚夫",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>还未封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>只是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>守时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许负</span>给他看相，说：\"您<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>后将封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>。封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八年（时长）</span>后将为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>，掌握国家大权，尊贵至极，在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>中无人可比。再过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>后您要饿死。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>笑道：\"我兄长已继承父亲的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>位了，即使他死，其子当继承，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>何谈封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>？再说如果真像您说的贵重，又怎会饿死？请指给我看。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许负</span>指着他的嘴说：\"有纵理纹入口，这是饿死的相<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>。\"过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，他兄长<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胜之</span>获罪，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>选择<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>诸子中贤能者，大家都推举<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>，续<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>后嗣。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "细柳军",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>大举入侵边境。于是任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宗正</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘礼</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，驻军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">祝兹侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐厉</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，驻军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘门</span>；以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，驻军<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">细柳</span>：以防备<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>人。皇上亲自慰劳军队。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘门</span>军，直接驰入，将领以下都骑马送迎。然后到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">细柳</span>军，军士官吏都披甲戴胄，兵器锐利，弓弩拉满。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的先锋到，进不去。先锋说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>就要到！\"军门的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>令说'军中只听<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>令，不听<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>诏'。\"过了一会儿，皇上到，又进不去。于是皇上派使者持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>传诏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>：\"我想入营慰劳军队。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>于是传令打开营门。营门士吏对随从<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车骑</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>约定，军中不得奔驰。\"于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>〘※按住缰绳慢行|按辔徐行〙。到营中，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>器作揖说：\"身穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲胄</span>的人不行跪拜礼，请以军<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>相见。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>被感动，表情严肃地凭靠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>前横木（行礼）。又让人传话说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>敬劳<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。\"行完礼仪离开。出营门后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都很惊讶。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>说：\"啊，这才真是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>！先前<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘门</span>的军营，就像儿戏一样，其将一定会被偷袭俘虏的。至于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>，怎能冒犯他！\"称赞了很久。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">月馀（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三军</span>都罢兵。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "文帝遗命",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span>将要驾崩时，告诫太子说：\"如果有紧急情况，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周亚夫</span>真可委以统兵重任。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>驾崩后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车骑将军</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "亚夫请战",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>由<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>升任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>，东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。自己向皇上请示说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵剽悍轻捷，〘※难与争锋〙。愿意把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地暂交给他们，断其粮道，才能制服。\"皇上同意。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "昌邑破吴",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>集结兵力，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军正<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>情势危急，请求救援。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>领兵向<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东北</span>奔赴<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>，坚守深沟高垒。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国每天派使者请求<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>出兵，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>按既定策略，不肯出动。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国上书<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>派使者诏令救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>不奉诏，坚守不出，而派轻骑兵<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">弓高侯</span>等<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">断</span>绝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵后方的粮道。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵缺粮饥饿，屡次挑战，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>终不出战。一天晚上，军中发生惊乱，内部互相攻击骚动，一直闹到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>的帐前。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>始终躺着不起。过一会儿，又安定了。后来<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军奔向营垒<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东南</span>角，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>命人加强<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西北</span>防备。不久吴军精兵果然奔向<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西北</span>，攻不进去。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵已饿，就引兵撤退。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>派精兵追击，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王濞</span>弃军，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>逃走，退保<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丹徒</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军乘胜，终于全部俘虏他们，招降其兵，悬赏千<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>购<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘濞\">吴王（刘濞）</span>头。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">月馀（时长）</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">越</span>人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘濞\">吴王（刘濞）</span>头来报。前后攻守共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三月（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>被平定。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>都认为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>的计谋是对的。从此<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>有了嫌隙。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "迁丞相忤旨",
      "text": "回朝后，恢复<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>官。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五岁（时长）</span>后，升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>非常倚重他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>废<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘荣\">栗太子（刘荣）</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>极力争谏，没有成功。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>从此疏远他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>每次朝见，常对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>讲<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>的坏话。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "争封王信",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>的兄长<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王信</span>可以<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封侯</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>推辞说：\"当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：南皮侯\">南皮（南皮侯）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦广国\">章武侯（窦广国）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先帝</span>都没有<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封侯</span>，到臣即位才<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>他们为侯。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王信\">信（王信）</span>还不能封。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>说：\"人主各在其时而行事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦长君</span>在世时，终究没能<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封侯</span>，死后才由其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭祖</span>获<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封侯</span>。我非常遗憾。皇帝赶快<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王信\">信（王信）</span>为侯吧！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>说：\"请允许我与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>商议。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>议此事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>说：\"高<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>立约'非<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>不得<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">王</span>，非有功不得<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">侯</span>。违背此约，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>共同讨伐他'。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王信\">信（王信）</span>虽是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>兄长，无功，却要<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封侯</span>，这是违背盟约的。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>沉默，作罢。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "争封匈奴",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐卢</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五人</span>降汉，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>想○封他们为侯以鼓励后来者。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>说：\"他们背叛其主来降<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>他们为侯，那怎么责备<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>中不守<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>的人呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>的议论不能采用。\"于是全<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐卢</span>等为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>因此称病。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，因病免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "大胾试心",
      "text": "不久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>在禁中，召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>来，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赐食</span>。只放一块大肉，没有切肉，又不放<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">筷子</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>心中不悦，回头让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尚席</span>官拿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">筷子</span>来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>看着他笑说：\"这不够你吃吗？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>免冠谢罪。皇上起身，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>快步离去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>目送他说：\"这种怏怏不满的人，不是辅佐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少主</span>的臣啊！\""
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "狱中不食而死",
      "text": "不久，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>之子为父买工官<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尚方</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">楯</span>五百件准备陪葬。雇工待遇差，不给<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>。雇工知他盗买县官器物，就怒而上书告变连累其子，事情牵连到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>。奏书呈上，皇上交给官吏处理。官吏按簿追问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>不答。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>骂道：\"我不用他了。\"召他到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>处。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>责问：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君侯</span>想谋反吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>说：\"我所买的器物，乃是葬器，为何说是谋反？\"官吏说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君侯</span>纵然不在地上造反，也是想在地下造反啊。\"官吏追逼越紧。起初官吏逮捕<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>想自杀，被<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>劝止，因而没死成，终于入了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>狱。他绝食<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五日（时长）</span>，吐血而死。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "续封平曲侯",
      "text": "绝国<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一岁（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>改封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>的其他儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周坚\">坚（周坚）</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平曲</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>，续<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>后嗣。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十九年（时长）</span>后去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周坚\">共侯（周坚）</span>。子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周建德\">建（周建德）</span>继承<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>侯，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十三年（时长）</span>后，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子太傅</span>。因进献酎<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>不合要求，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>获罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "条侯果饿死",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>果然饿死。死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>才<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王信</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">盖侯</span>。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周勃</span>最初是<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布</span>衣百姓时，朴实之人，才能不过平庸。等到跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>平定<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，居<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>之位，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸吕</span>欲作乱，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>匡扶国家之难，使之恢复正道。虽然<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>，又怎能超过他！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>用兵，威重持久，坚执刀刃，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>又怎能超过！可惜他自满而不学，守<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>不逊让，终至穷困。可悲啊！"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>辅<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，质厚敦厚。 初击<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>东，又围<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">尸北</span>。 所攻必克，所讨必胜。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伏诛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>国。 事生送死，推功藏德。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>回府，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下狱</span>。 继相<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span>，绍封<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平曲</span>。 可惜贤将，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span>〖=相继受辱！"
